import React from 'react'
import {Button, Form ,FormControl, Stack} from 'react-bootstrap'
const SendBtn = () => {
  return (
    <Stack direction='horizontal' gap={3} style={{padding:"10px"}}>

        <FormControl
            type="text"
            placeholder='Enter your message here'
            />
        <Button>Send</Button>
        </Stack>
  )
}

export default SendBtn
